ass=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-scope None ng-not-empty\"><div class=\"video-content active\"><p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p><span class=\"icon-video\"></span></div><div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/463491744\"></iframe></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"fV06p\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5><b>Lesson Summary</b></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"AriyY\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">When organizations start to value ethics in terms of expressions of values, behaviour or integrity in the character of people, there are visible differences that can be seen in employees' behaviour<br></li><li class=\"\">Organizational culture means, a shared understanding of all the values, expectations, the philosophy or the mission and the vision of a corporation</li><li class=\"\">The formal approach has multiple components such as mission statements, code of ethics, risk-benefit analysis, some designated posts or forums for managing ethics, ethics consultants, stakeholder engagement, and certain accounting, auditing and reporting practices<br></li><li class=\"\">The biggest outcome of the social risk is reputational damage which reflects even in the market</li><li class=\"\">Many companies realize that external professional ethics consultants are necessary to address certain areas of ethics management within the organization</li><li class=\"\">A corporation is accountable to its society and stakeholders</li><li class=\"\">Ethical misconduct in a corporation can happen at various levels such as individual, interpersonal, group and organizational</li><li class=\"\">Ethics can be applied using the top-down approach or the casuistry reasoning&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\">An ethical dilemma is a situation where there is a conflict between two competing moral obligations or duties</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"U1s4e\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5><b>Learning Outcomes</b></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"mBppc\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><b>Upon completion of this module, you should be able to:</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"zqv08\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Define&nbsp;corporate governance</li><li class=\"\">Outline some very famous examples of the failure of corporate governance</li><li class=\"\">Describe corporate governance as an agency problem</li><li class=\"\">List the key elements that determine the quality of corporate governance</li><li class=\"\">Analyze specific areas of concern in corporate governance as well as countermeasures</li><li class=\"\">Explain the issues of excessive remuneration of top executives</li><li class=\"\">Outline the problems related to mergers and acquisition</li><li class=\"\">Discuss the concept of&nbsp;Socially Responsible Investment (SRI)</li><li class=\"\">Explain shareholder democracy and activism</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"FwvZh\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h5><b>Corporate Governance Failures</b></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"BKfSn\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list listed selected-class video-box   border active,\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-scope None ng-not-empty\"><div class=\"video-content active\"><p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p><span class=\"icon-video\"></span></div><div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/463544748\"></iframe></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintr